scene.message:
Principal Oishi: {ctl0f:1}!{nl}
You're safe! I'm{nl}
so relieved...!{waitkey}{clearbox}If anything happened tomy dear students...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
I worry so...{waitkey}{ret}

Vice Principal: Outrageous!{nl}
If anything goes wrong,{nl}
the school bears blame!{waitkey}{clearbox}And then WE get{nl}
disciplined!{waitkey}{clearbox}If only the students had{nl}
gone home earlier...{waitkey}What a miserable wretch{nl}
I am!{waitkey}{ret}

Principal Oishi: I hear{nl}
you're looking into{nl}
the Snow Queen...{wait_fr:48}{wait_fr:21}{nl}
Let me tell you all.{waitkey}{clearbox}Our school's Snow Queen{nl}
has always been performed{nl}
wearing a mask.{waitkey}{clearbox}But that mask carried{nl}
a troubling rumor{nl}
that never went away.{waitkey}{clearbox}People started saying{nl}
the queen's mask{nl}
was cursed.{waitkey}{clearbox}Even I didn't believe it{nl}
until eight years ago...{waitkey}{clearbox}The last Snow Queen{nl}
was Ms. Saeko.{waitkey}{ret}

Principal Oishi: Eight{nl}
years ago...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Ms. Saeko lost her{nl}
best friend.{waitkey}{clearbox}If only I had noticed{nl}
sooner...{wait_fr:32} If only she{nl}
hadn't worn that mask...{waitkey}{clearbox}...{wait_fr:21} The mask was{nl}
put away and stored{nl}
in the gym after that.{waitkey}{clearbox}Please don't bring up{nl}
Ms. Saeko's{nl}
painful past.{waitkey}{ret}

Vice Principal: ...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
The principal is just{nl}
joking, kid. Don't{nl}
believe a word of it!{waitkey}{ret}

{color:3}Principal Oishi.{nl}
Headmistress of St. Hermelin.{nl}
A woman who loves children{nl}
and flowers alike.{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Vice Principal Hannya.{nl}
Also called "Hannya."{nl}
Notoriously strict and{nl}
deeply unpopular.{waitkey}{ret}

Principal Oishi: I don't{nl}
want to lose any more{nl}
dear students...{wait_fr:37}{nl}
Please take care.{waitkey}{ret}

Vice Principal: What now?{nl}
I'm busy —{nl}
get out of here!{waitkey}{ret}

Principal Oishi: The Snow{nl}
Queen mask... could it be{nl}
connected to all this?{waitkey}{clearbox}Surely not... But{nl}
{ctl0f:1}, stay away{nl}
from the gym storage.{waitkey}{ret}
